    <summary>Replica of Nintendo’s The Legend of Zelda and a game editor</summary>
    <description>**Zelda Classic** is a tribute to Nintendo’s 1991 video game, The Legend of Zelda. It is an exact replica of the game, but is also comes with a game editor called ZQuest that allows you to make completely new quests, with either the same or enhanced graphics, or you can play the many quests that other people have made.

### Installation, upgrade and uninstallation

The default installation directory is `C:\Games\Zelda Classic\`.

Custom quests and save data will *not* be removed on uninstallation. Settings *will* be removed.

Upgrade, force installation and uninstallation will not proceed if zelda.exe or zquest.exe is running.</description>
